使用同样的步骤方法给Lena带上眼镜¶

In [23]:
# 墨镜
r = cv2.selectROI(lena)
cv2.destroyAllWindows()
x, y = r[0], r[1]
w, h = r[2], r[3]
roi = lena[y : y + h, x : x + w]
glasses = cv2.imread('../cvimages/ch03/glasses.jpg')
glasses = cv2.resize(glasses, (w, h))
gray = cv2.cvtColor(glasses, cv2.COLOR_BGR2GRAY)
_, mask = cv2.threshold(gray, 220, 255, cv2.THRESH_BINARY_INV)
foreground = cv2.bitwise_and(glasses, glasses, mask=mask)
mask_lena = cv2.bitwise_not(mask)
background = cv2.bitwise_and(roi, roi, mask = mask_lena)
lena_glass = cv2.add(foreground, background)
lena[y:y+h, x:x+w] = lena_glass

plt.imshow(lena[:, :, ::-1])
Out[23]:
<matplotlib.image.AxesImage at 0x1df5c3374a8>
